extends ComponentTypeImpl
implements VirtualProcessorType
    An implementation of the model object 'Virtual Processor Type'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Owned Feature
    • Owned Data Port
    • Owned Event Data Port
    • Owned Event Port
    • Owned Subprogram Access
    • Owned Subprogram Group Access
